Description: An intelligent toolkit for automated R data package creation.
    Evolved from washr, fairenough minimizes manual intervention by automating
    data processing, AI-powered dictionary generation, documentation creation,
    and publication workflows. Features chainable functions and a unified
    pipeline from raw data to published package.
